---

<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="proof-inner fade-up">
      <div class="section-label">Why Archway</div>
      <h2>Built for Independent Insurance Agencies &mdash; Not Generic IT Clients</h2>
      <div class="proof-grid">
        <div class="proof-card">
          <div class="proof-icon orange">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Insurance-Native</h4>
          <p>We only work with independent agencies. Every checklist, every recommendation, and every project we deliver is designed around how your business actually operates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-card">
          <div class="proof-icon blue">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm-3.06 16L7.4 14.46l1.41-1.41 2.12 2.12 4.67-4.67 1.41 1.41L10.94 18zM13 9V3.5L18.5 9H13z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Compliance-Aware</h4>
          <p>From NYDFS to carrier cybersecurity requirements, we stay current so you don't have to. These checklists are built around what matters for your agency's risk posture right now.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-card">
          <div class="proof-icon orange">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>No Obligation</h4>
          <p>Download the checklist, run through it on your own, and use it however you want. If you find gaps and want help addressing them, we're here. If not, the checklist is still yours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .proof-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .proof-inner h2 {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .proof-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .proof-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
    border-color: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.3);
  }

  .proof-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .proof-icon svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
  }

  .proof-icon.orange {
    background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.12);
  }
  .proof-icon.orange svg {
    fill: var(--orange);
  }

  .proof-icon.blue {
    background: rgba(41, 63, 80, 0.12);
  }
  .proof-icon.blue svg {
    fill: var(--blue);
  }

  .proof-card h4 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .proof-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
